三、教學目標 Objectives


This course is designed to nurture in students an interest in the Chinese Mainland affairs and cross-strait relations. Through an in-depth analysis of China’s politico-economic developments as well as the past trajectory of cross-strait relations, students are expected to learn to appreciate the nature and potential future trends of these relations.　


四、課程內容 Course Description


●整體敘述 Overall Descriptiona. This class will be conducted in a manner befitting a seminar. Interactions between the instructor and students are expected and encouraged. Topics to be discussed will be presented with the aid of PowerPoint slide show. Audio/video materials may also be shown whenever available and deemed necessary.b. Each week students are required to collect at least 2 pieces of current economic/business/trade news concerning mainland China from the mass media and share the news with fellow students. 30 minutes of class time each week will be allocated for this endeavor.

